    <string name="inspire_prompt_relax">Soft, low-energy music for unwinding; calm rather than sad, with gentle vocals or instrumentals.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_workout">High-energy music with a strong beat for sustained exercise; avoid slow songs and keep the momentum moving.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_sad">Restrained, emotionally resonant sad music for a quiet night alone; avoid anything overly aggressive.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_party">Bright, danceable music for a party with friends; clear beats and energy that gradually builds.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_sleep">Quiet, low-dynamic music for falling asleep; prefer ambient or instrumental tracks without sudden loud changes.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_surprise">Choose a varied but naturally flowing mix from my local library, balancing favorites with less-played songs.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_focus">Steady, unobtrusive music for focused work; favor instrumentals, consistent pacing and minimal vocal distraction.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_commute">Bright, rhythmic music for the commute; energizing without becoming noisy, with a clear forward pulse.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_rain">Warm, intimate music for sitting by the window on a rainy day; gentle texture, moderate tempo and no harsh peaks.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_morning">Fresh, optimistic music for waking up; start gently, then build into a clear and lively rhythm.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_night_drive">Atmospheric music for a night drive; deep rhythm, spacious production and a smooth continuous flow.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_cafe">Relaxed cafe ambience with warm vocals, jazz, soul or acoustic textures; social but never distracting.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_nostalgia">Songs that feel nostalgic and familiar; emotional but not overly sad, with memorable melodies.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_weekend">Loose, sunny weekend music; comfortable mid-tempo grooves, easy vocals and an unhurried mood.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_date_night">Warm, elegant music for a quiet date; intimate vocals, soft rhythm and a romantic atmosphere without being dramatic.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_reading">Mostly instrumental music for reading; low dynamics, stable rhythm and enough space to keep attention on the page.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_road_trip">Open, uplifting music for a road trip; strong choruses, steady momentum and smooth transitions between styles.</string>
    <string name="inspire_prompt_hidden_gems">Surface excellent but less-played songs from my library; keep the sequence coherent and avoid overusing familiar favorites.</string>

